Package: surfscape
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Your Own Way to Navigate the Web with Freedom (static build)
 Surfscape is a modern web browser built with PyQt6 that provides:
 .
  * Advanced ad-blocking with EasyList support
  * Built-in Claude AI assistant for web research
  * Developer tools with console, elements, network monitoring
  * Private browsing mode
  * Bookmark and history management
  * Download manager
  * Find in page functionality
  * Source code viewer
  * Performance monitoring
  * Customizable themes and settings
  * Session restoration
 .
 This package contains a statically-built executable with all dependencies
 bundled, so no additional Python packages are required.
